headline: SYF Ties Up to Offer Two Credit Cards: Higher Net Interest Income Ahead?
summary: Synchrony teams up with OnePay and Walmart to launch Mastercard-powered credit cards, offering flexible financing options and boosting U.S. consumers' purchasing power from this fall.
